WWE NXT (6/17) Viewership Down, Key Demo Rating Up Against NHL Stanley Cup Finals Competition
By Skylar Russell,
5 hours agoViewership and ratings information for the June 17 episode of WWE NXT. Programming Insider reports that WWE NXT on June 17 scored 660,000 viewers on the CW Network. This number is down from the 726,000 viewers the show posted on June 10. Tuesday's episode scored a 0.16 rating in the...
